class.name: gd_Aspect_FillMethod
class.brief_description: Defines the fill methods to write bitmaps in a window.
class.description: Binding for the Open CASCADE Aspect_FillMethod enum. This class provides the fill methods used to write bitmaps in a window. Note: This is an enum wrapper for Godot GDExtension and does not wrap any underlying C++ object.

constant.name: FM_CENTERED
constant.description: Bitmap is centered in the window.

constant.name: FM_TILED
constant.description: Bitmap is tiled in the window.

constant.name: FM_STRETCH
constant.description: Bitmap is stretched to fit the window.
